# Trim the quest-processor image build context (was ~3 GB → slow/timeout-prone on the
# deploy runner). These dirs aren't needed to build or run the server. NOTE: do not exclude
# whole workspace members — pnpm needs every package.json for lockfile resolution. The
# entries below are VCS metadata, build output, mobile shells, tests, and docs-site (which
# pnpm-workspace.yaml already excludes via `!docs-site`).
.git
**/.next
**/.open-next
**/coverage
apps/client/ios
apps/client/android
apps/client/e2e
docs-site
.playwright-mcp
